about1:
I am here for my curiosity, and I have insomnia these days. Since I have time at night, why not?

And what I need to tell is I hate to take photos! Sorry, in this way, I am not a typical Asian girl ;) Don't ask me for other pics. I know who I am, and I will be more charming if we have the chance to see each other in the real life.

I consider myself as girl-child, will be always curious about everything (yes, I am an international student, to be here, it is already my adventure), be happy and willing to learn.

Some boys consider I am cute, some think I am sexy, you guys have different standards, I can't tell. Everything is just a feeling, it is what about an attraction: physical and spiritual.

What is going next? We will see.

I am tried, I'd better go.
about2:
I don't have a type, if I like you, I like you.
Vice versa.
Come as you are.
